<GUIClass name="SHP_RORODeckDefinitionForm" id="c94e9242-eec2-41a7-97c3-13d810d67879">
    <superclass name="CM_BaseForm"/>
    <transient/>
    <subclassTransientAllowed/>
    <transientAllowed/>
    <text>

SCALE
####

1 foot = 3 pixels
8 feet = 24 pixels
20 feet = 60 pixels
40 feet = 120 pixels

1 metre = 10 pixels (ROROStructurePixelsPerMetre)
6 metre = 60 pixels (20 feet)
2.4 metre = 24 pixels (8 feet)

The polygons are the layout and so are stored in centimetres. These are converted to pixels.

10 centimetres = 1 pixel;

</text>
